BEGIN_PGML_SOLUTION
We need to keep our focus on [`b`] and take algebra steps that bring us closer to isolating [`b\text{.}`]

[```\newcommand{\amp}{&}
\begin{aligned}
A \amp= \frac12bh\\
2A \amp= bh\\
\frac{2A}{h} \amp= b\\
b \amp= \frac{2A}{h}
\end{aligned}
```]

